Dialogue: 10,0:00:01.56,0:00:05.19,Default,Phanora,0,0,0,,Only the undead can see its light.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:05.19,0:00:08.65,Default,Phanora,0,0,0,,And in the eyes of those who have lost\N their reason through neglect,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:08.65,0:00:10.80,Default,Phanora,0,0,0,,it outshines all else.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.61,0:00:15.91,Default,Phanora,0,0,0,,I chose a deserted area to minimize the risk,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:16.70,0:00:19.87,Default,Phanora,0,0,0,,but it appears we unintentionally \Nhit the nail on the head.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:21.03,0:00:23.68,Default,Johan,0,0,0,,Oh, the trail keeps going this way.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:28.44,0:00:30.48,Default,Necromancer,0,0,0,,With necromancy,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:31.50,0:00:34.95,Default,Necromancer,0,0,0,,no parting lasts forever.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:39.20,0:00:40.64,Default,Jeff,0,0,0,,What have you done?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:41.77,0:00:43.68,Default,Jeff,0,0,0,,What have you done?!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:44.35,0:00:47.14,Default,Necromancer,0,0,0,,This will suffice for him,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:47.14,0:00:52.99,Default,Necromancer,0,0,0,,but as for you, despite my efforts,\N I couldn't learn a thing about you.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:52.99,0:00:56.96,Default,Necromancer,0,0,0,,I'll avail myself of a bargaining chip now.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:03.75,0:01:04.79,Default,Phanora,0,0,0,,Johan!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:06.40,0:01:10.09,Default,Necromancer,0,0,0,,Do as I say, and you'll see him again soon.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:10.56,0:01:12.94,Default,Necromancer,0,0,0,,Now, follow me.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.87,0:03:25.43,Flashback,Coroner,0,0,0,,Um... Performing her autopsy \Nmust be hard for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.96,0:03:27.19,Flashback,Coroner,0,0,0,,Why don't I take over?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.13,0:03:29.65,Flashback,Necromancer,0,0,0,,There's no need.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.28,0:03:32.83,Flashback,Necromancer,0,0,0,,I'm perfectly fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.83,0:03:34.85,Flashback,Coroner,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.34,0:03:43.18,Flashback,Necromancer,0,0,0,,How hideous.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.28,0:03:51.64,Flashback,Necromancer,0,0,0,,Mireille, I shall bring you back\N with flawless beauty.
